From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: lynxtron <lynxtron@lynxjs.com>
Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add string include for windows build

Fix Windows build error caused by missing <string> include in
src/base/unique_fd.hpp. The file uses std::wstring in DirCacheEntry
but doesn't include <string> header, causing compilation errors
with libc++.

---
 src/base/unique_fd.hpp | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/src/base/unique_fd.hpp b/src/base/unique_fd.hpp
index 1e98584..c4737d5 100644
--- a/src/base/unique_fd.hpp
+++ b/src/base/unique_fd.hpp
@@ -16,6 +16,7 @@
 #include <map>
 #include <mutex>
 #include <optional>
+#include <string>
 #else  // SKITY_WIN
 #include <dirent.h>
 #include <unistd.h>
--
